text: Hanna Grages (8 December 1922 - 27 August 2010) was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:2010 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Verden an der Aller
